response.overview: March 27th, 2009 :: It is the biggest pro-wrestling tournament of 2009, and Chikara's hallmark, the King of Trios! Sixteen teams, each comprised of 3 wrestlers, vie to win the tournament and ultimate bragging rights. Night 1 features all 8 of the opening round tournament matches! First round matches featured:  1.Team EPIC WAR vs The F1rst Family  2. The Osirian Portal vs Team PWG  3. The Roughnecks vs Team Uppercut  4. Team CZW vs Da Soul Touchaz  5. F.I.S.T. vs The Death Match Kings  6. The Future Is Now vs Team DDT  7. Incoherence vs The Masters Of A Thousand Holds  8. The UnStable vs The Cold Front.
response.title: Chikara King Of Trios 2009 - Night 1
